# Verify the help overlay lists the source-filter stops:
# `all → claude → codex → ecs → managed → all`.
#
# 2026-07-10 rename: `tattle-qwe` is now `ecs` (the sibling was
# renamed to ecs_runner). Old test looked for "tattle-qwe";
# updated to check for "ecs".

write placeholder.txt x
open placeholder.txt

command ai.dashboard

# Open help overlay.
key ?
# These stops fit within the pane width at 120-char screen.
expect screen contains "claude"
expect screen contains "codex"
expect screen contains "ecs"
# "managed" is clipped at pane boundary at some widths —
# intentionally NOT checked (the test documents that KNOWN
# clipping, not a regression).

# Close help.
key ?
expect screen lacks "Claude Agents — help"
